    "name": "太阳的尽头",
    "steam_appid": 912840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/9643be24eee1361afb139b27db321a90.avif?t=1771977573\" width=841 height=128 /></span><strong>成为神话生物和超自然力量的追踪者。</strong> 掌控时间之火的力量，探索古老的土地，解开不同寻常的谜题，并体验非凡的冒险，这一切都是更宏大、引人入胜的故事的一部分。 找到你的目标，在神秘的村庄中平息时间的混乱，揭开隐藏其中的秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91edb31b5584a4cb264861a7b6076921.poster.avif?t=1771977573\" width=890 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91edb31b5584a4cb264861a7b6076921.webm?t=1771977573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/91edb31b5584a4cb264861a7b6076921.mp4?t=1771977573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/79d5dd01136ef42b75cf45c7e203cbf9.avif?t=1771977573\" width=841 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你是一位掌控时间的斯拉夫火焰巫师。</strong> 你来到一个现实已经被扭曲的村庄，那里的村民只留下了未熄的炉火。<strong>凭借与火焰沟通的能力，你能看到别人看不见的事物——踪迹、神话生物以及往昔事件的灵魂。</strong> 你是否能运用自己的力量阻止古老的力量，并改变居民的命运？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/3de496d8ea86fdb3fc81524a506bd2c9.poster.avif?t=1771977573\" width=890 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/3de496d8ea86fdb3fc81524a506bd2c9.webm?t=1771977573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/3de496d8ea86fdb3fc81524a506bd2c9.mp4?t=1771977573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/8b6de2631ab1ca44877910cd4e6ebd25.avif?t=1771977573\" width=841 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《太阳的尽头》</strong>是一款充满神秘气息的第一人称冒险探索游戏，背景设定在斯拉夫幻想世界。游戏的核心玩法围绕使用魔法地图探索开放世界，并与篝火建立联系。每一次连接都会揭示普通人无法看到的新线索和事件。<strong>完全点燃的篝火将成为穿越时间的门户。</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/60c5318f564915693d251df17f4ef55a.avif?t=1771977573\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/7159b93bfab232f75b8afe01c737b1a0.avif?t=1771977573\" width=841 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/865b15b3580a5d6d9d711e338942e384.avif?t=1771977573\" width=841 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/f83e0a4fdb470af0bb01198017913199.avif?t=1771977573\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/b32428c8c9b4304ce866b93e6d576e0f.avif?t=1771977573\" width=841 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/2dd11a32c84b7fc1d8426eaf08f2fe45.webp?t=1771977573\" width=841 height=9 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/55733ee5a44ab88619c59623c31808e4.avif?t=1771977573\" width=735 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>1. 追踪 – 与火焰融为一体，让它引领你</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身为超自然的追踪者。追随神话生物的足迹，揭示隐藏在燃烧篝火中的秘密。你连接的每一个火堆，都是一次独特的调查，充满不同寻常的谜题，并作为通往古代斯拉夫世界的大门——一个充满魔法、奇幻生物、神话与被遗忘仪式的国度。你点燃的每一团时间之火，都是更宏大故事的一部分。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/c6ebc037cda2f2ccda5287c854db07a6.avif?t=1771977573\" width=1560 height=646 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/d5bc42643255046e4654db6e224494eb.avif?t=1771977573\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>2. 唤醒力量 – 使用火焰穿越时间，塑造人类的命运</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受时间之火的力量。影响英雄们的命运之路——让事件重回正轨，发现史诗故事的新片段。穿越四个相隔多年的季节。见证同样的英雄在不同人生阶段中的经历，在最盛大的斯拉夫节日里。时间与篝火紧密交织。你的行动会影响周围的世界——带来改变，并仔细观察其后果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/d4198a146670c991741f2e9087ad9ac8.avif?t=1771977573\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/07b7a1f1df5a4a11dad0a4399f8354ec.avif?t=1771977573\" width=1560 height=647 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>3. 调查 – 探索一个源自现实世界与博物馆珍宝的神秘村庄</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百件博物馆文物和整座建筑，通过摄影测量技术从现实世界带入游戏，为你开启一片每个细节都意义非凡的土地。自由探索古老的村庄及其独特的环境。在探索这个开放世界的过程中，进行一场植根于斯拉夫神话的超自然调查——比以往任何时候都更真实、更具沉浸感。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/0642dfed15c51f88bc967ba59ff1f8fd.avif?t=1771977573\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/8dc6d41d5558a65b13a888aead07e88f.avif?t=1771977573\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/912840/extras/67fb6a499cb9cb2076a97c48321726ae.avif?t=1771977573\" width=1560 height=646 /></span></p>",
